        "endTime": 10295,
        "slowStartTime": 11302,
        "slowEndTime": 15667
    },
    {
        "text": "Most of it is hogwash.",
        "startTime": 10732,
        "endTime": 12043,
        "slowStartTime": 16248,
        "slowEndTime": 18289
    },
    {
        "text": "But most of them don't really believe in training, in building teams and investing in people.",
        "startTime": 13177,
        "endTime": 20219,
        "slowStartTime": 19916,
        "slowEndTime": 30554
    },
    {
        "text": "Investing in people is the whole ball game.",
        "startTime": 20872,
        "endTime": 23879,
        "slowStartTime": 31458,
        "slowEndTime": 36043
    },
    {
        "text": "When you invest in people and when you give them your trust,...",
        "startTime": 24417,
        "endTime": 28599,
        "slowStartTime": 36775,
        "slowEndTime": 43123
    },
    {
        "text": "...and they give you their trust, and you both drive towards a common vision...,",
        "startTime": 28751,
        "endTime": 34220,
        "slowStartTime": 43277,
        "slowEndTime": 51555
    },
    {
        "text": "...and you explain to them what's in it for them,...",
        "startTime": 34715,
        "endTime": 37044,
        "slowStartTime": 52223,
        "slowEndTime": 55791
    },
    {
        "text": "...not just where you're going, where you're going, yes,...",
        "startTime": 37847,
        "endTime": 40779,
        "slowStartTime": 56920,
        "slowEndTime": 61393
    },
    {
        "text": "...but what's in it for them to go there.",
        "startTime": 41070,
        "endTime": 42862,
        "slowStartTime": 61755,
        "slowEndTime": 64518
    },
    {
        "text": "You build great teams with great results.",
        "startTime": 43682,
        "endTime": 46775,
        "slowStartTime": 65673,
        "slowEndTime": 70387
    },
    {
        "text": "And that's what this is all about.",
        "startTime": 47291,
        "endTime": 48687,
        "slowStartTime": 71087,
        "slowEndTime": 73256
    },
    {
        "text": "And people don't get that.",
        "startTime": 48779,
        "endTime": 50002,
        "slowStartTime": 73319,
        "slowEndTime": 75228
    },
    {
        "text": "People don't understand that you've got to invest in training.",
        "startTime": 50407,
        "endTime": 53994,
        "slowStartTime": 75761,
        "slowEndTime": 81216
    },
    {
        "text": "You've got to invest, you've got to get the culture that's common,...",
        "startTime": 54579,
